Package: treedrought
Title: Calculated drought indices and models drought recovery.
Version: 0.9.0.0000
Authors@R: 
    person("Vinicius", "Manvailer", , "vmgoncal@ualberta.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6529-4474"))
Description: Uses tree ring data and monthly climate data to identify ecologically defined drought events, calculate resilience indices and model a standardized recovery capacity of trees/sites.
Depends: 
    data.table,
    R (>= 2.10),
    SPEI
